{"id":"8003","user":{"id":"117492","nickname":"亦舟","avatar_url":"https://static.codemao.cn/FsEnKJerhNpeEolozd_6MDHX3Y1e?attname=","subject_id":0,"work_shop_name":"","work_shop_level":0,"wuhan_medal":false,"has_signed":false},"title":"【少院士讲堂】 Java零基础入门教程 P2：数据类型与运算符","content":"<p><p style=\"text-align: center;\"><font size=\"5\" color=\"#ff00ff\">【前言】</font></p>\n<p><font size=\"3\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;今天给大家继续带来Java教程，那么废话不多说，开始吧。</font></p>\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\"><font size=\"5\" color=\"#008000\">【正式开始】</font></p>\n<p><font size=\"4\">&nbsp; &nbsp; 一、基本数据类型</font><br></p>\n<p><font size=\"3\">&nbsp; &nbsp; Java注重类型，如果类型出错是过不了编译器这关的（好像编程语言都这样），Java的数据类型有2大种：内置数据类型与引用数据类型。下面我们来看一下内置数据类型：</font></p>\n<p><font size=\"3\">&nbsp; &nbsp; boolean：布尔值，true或false</font></p>\n<p><font size=\"3\">&nbsp; &nbsp; char：16位，0~65535<br></font></p>\n<p><font size=\"3\">&nbsp; &nbsp; byte：数值，8位，-128~127</font></p>\n<p><font size=\"3\">&nbsp; &nbsp; short：数值，<span>16位，-32768~32767</span></font></p>\n<p><font size=\"3\">&nbsp; &nbsp;&nbsp;int：数值，<span>32位，</span><span>-2147483648~2147483647</span></font></p>\n<p><font size=\"3\">&nbsp; &nbsp; long：数值，64位，数值范围很大，就不列举了</font></p>\n<p><font size=\"3\">&nbsp; &nbsp; float：浮点，32位，范围可变<br></font></p>\n<p><font size=\"3\">&nbsp; &nbsp; double：浮点，64位，范围可变<br></font></p>\n<p><font size=\"3\">&nbsp; &nbsp; 接下来我们先看一个列子：<br></font></p>\n<p>&nbsp; &nbsp;&nbsp;<img src=\"https://static.codemao.cn/FkdrLUtPBq2SIzqLZRz6bMCZkzX0\"><font size=\"3\"><br></font></p>\n<p><font size=\"3\">&nbsp; &nbsp; 这个时候的输出结果是：</font></p>\n<p><font size=\"3\">&nbsp; &nbsp;&nbsp;<img src=\"https://static.codemao.cn/FhVzmcvWqJkjh0V7qul2UC6G6MBe\"><br></font></p>\n<p><font size=\"3\">&nbsp; &nbsp; 大家会发现输出的是：666</font></p>\n<p><font size=\"3\">&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; 233<br></font></p>\n<p><font size=\"3\">&nbsp; &nbsp; 而不是：666233，原因就在语句println上，print是紧接着后面打印，println是换行打印。<br></font></p>\n<p><font size=\"3\">&nbsp; &nbsp; 这里x是int类型，如果给变量赋值其他类型的话，那么编译器就不乐意了：</font><br></p>\n<p><font size=\"3\">&nbsp; &nbsp;&nbsp;<img src=\"https://static.codemao.cn/FhbXBOn2XXM0p4cYIssVj5mguP67\"><br></font></p>\n<p><font size=\"3\"><br></font></p>\n<p><font size=\"4\">二、Java运算符</font></p>\n<p><font size=\"3\">&nbsp; &nbsp; 每一种编程语言肯定少不了运算，Java就给我们提供了很多（好吧，其实不是很多）运算符，先来看一下各个运算符的作用：<br></font></p>\n<p><font size=\"3\">&nbsp; &nbsp;&nbsp;</font><img src=\"https://static.codemao.cn/FokGbV5F1dr4kPNE0nUGMPC14HB0\"><font size=\"3\"><br></font></p>\n<p><font size=\"3\">&nbsp; &nbsp; Java还可以做大数字运算，</font>此时我们使用了long，Java中的长整型，<span>看一下这个列子：</span></p>\n<p>&nbsp; &nbsp;&nbsp;<img src=\"https://static.codemao.cn/FrpeBH9T4BQ0lpBt3rqnZZ1Y5X9V\"><br></p>\n<p>&nbsp; &nbsp;&nbsp;<img src=\"https://static.codemao.cn/FmsITKCf2aR0rQrRuTYQjuHuJWNr\"><br></p>\n<p>&nbsp; &nbsp;&nbsp;<font size=\"1\"><u>(哇，真心强大)</u></font></p>\n<p><br></p></p>","board_id":"2","board_name":"积木编程乐园","updated_at":1517617201,"created_at":1512652489,"n_views":197,"n_replies":3,"n_comments":0,"is_authorized":false,"is_featured":true,"is_hotted":false,"is_pinned":false,"tutorial_flag":0,"ask_help_flag":0}